com.vaadin.event.MethodEventSource, com.vaadin.terminal.Paintable, com.vaadin.terminal.Sizeable, com.vaadin.terminal.VariableOwner, com.vaadin.ui.Component, com.vaadin.ui.ComponentContainer, EntityEditor, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener
public class ExpertForm
extends com.vaadin.ui.CustomComponent
implements EntityEditor

Form for editing an entity. The layout of this form can be edited with the Vaadin Visual Editor. Fields are automatically bound to container data sources and item properties based on their names (propertyId + "Field") in the aspect. Implementing methods with the same name as used in the aspect allows "overriding" functionality as such methods replace those from the aspect.
